# Design System

**Fontes:** `.ai/design/tokens.md`, `.ai/design/ui-contracts.md`, `.ai/design/components.md`

## Tokens ERP (CSS)
Usar sempre — suportam dark mode:
- `var(--foreground)`, `var(--card)`, `var(--card-foreground)`
- `var(--primary-600)`, `var(--border)`, `var(--input-background)`
- `var(--spacing-1)` a `var(--spacing-6)` (base 8px)
- Erros: `color-mix(in srgb, var(--error) 10%, transparent)`

## Botões
Classes em `styles.css`:
```html
<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Salvar</button>
<button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">Cancelar</button>
<button type="button" class="btn btn-danger">Excluir</button>
```

## Páginas
- **Listagem:** `page-container`, `page-header`, `page-actions` (ver ui-contracts.md)
- **Detalhe:** `feature-detail__header`, `__back`, `__title`, `__card`, `__info`, `__actions`

Referência de página de detalhe:
@src/app/features/authorization/pages/role-detail.page.html
@src/app/features/authorization/pages/role-detail.page.css

## Proibido
- Cores hardcoded (#fff, #333, etc.)
- `app-button` ou componentes inexistentes
